Package: scoccer
Type: Package
Title: Enables the use of scottish soccer data from football-data.co.uk
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Steffen Bank
Maintainer: Steffen Bank <shok3y@gmail.com>
Description: The package allows easy integration with historical standard data of the Scottish Premiership and Championship. Additionally modeling functions are implemented.
